sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(225, 245, 255) Fleet Customer
        participant User as Fleet Customer (Browser)
    end
    box rgb(230, 126, 34) Spryker
        participant Yves as Yves Storefront
        participant Checkout as Checkout (Zed)
        participant OMS as OMS State Machine
        participant Notify as FMAT OMS Commands
        participant Mail as OrderConfirmationMail command
    end
    box rgb(149, 165, 166) External
        participant FMAT as FMAT
        participant SMTP as SMTP
    end

    User->>Yves: Proceed to checkout
    Yves->>Checkout: Submit (Invoice — no PSP)
    Checkout->>Checkout: Validate cart + place order
    Note over Checkout: No approval workflow (POC)
    Checkout->>OMS: Order created -> initial state
    Checkout-->>Yves: Order placed
    Yves-->>User: Order confirmation page

    par Async, fire-and-forget (POC)
        OMS->>Notify: Event: order created
        Notify->>FMAT: POST order-created notification [async]
        Note over Notify,FMAT: Fire-and-forget — no retry/error handling (POC)
    and
        OMS->>Mail: Event: send confirmation
        Mail->>SMTP: Send order confirmation email
        SMTP-->>User: Confirmation email
    end

    Note over OMS,FMAT: FUTURE — 2nd async call: payment + activation date
